{"tid":1079821,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇韻姿加國發展受限制","createTime":"2019-03-27T07:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T09:06:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"213dff606e1761432f14a53cd0df99ea2cb8c51b","tid":1079821,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"憑處境劇《愛．回家之開心速遞》「熊心如」一角成功入屋的藝人蘇韻姿（Andrea），日前接受東網節目《娛場》訪問，重提在加拿大曾因華人身份受歧視，失去不少演出機會，至今仍令她耿耿於懷。她指當時與弟弟因樣貌可愛而被選入當地的廣告公司：「之後去過無數次試鏡，每次見到自己都係唯一嘅華人，而佢哋嘅角色根本一早設定畀外國人，亦唔會畀機會華人，但我都照去想挑戰自己，畀人知我係有實力；被拒絕過無數次，你亦都唔會再驚。」她透露最終同事叫她回港發展，因認為沒有種族限制，機會較多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PLBT1Aj2BmTS63V4WuPc2A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/05338a3574b376e69856e4ee812e9682\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPLBT1Aj2BmTS63V4WuPc2A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F05338a3574b376e69856e4ee812e9682&h=4bf4bd5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E8%98%87%E9%9F%BB%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6-214500507.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2598%2587%25E9%259F%25BB%25E5%25A7%25BF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6-214500507.html&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5YleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=0a9fd458\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E8%98%87%E9%9F%BB%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6-214500507.html</a>"},{"pid":"cd5b3dd63c2831984043c14fac2d3b204c25e42b","tid":1079821,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"好彩佢黎香港,唔係無得J佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.